data.description: Welcome to This Charming 3/4 Bedroom 2 Full Bath Tudor Style Home That Seamlessly Blends Old-World Charm with Modern Updates. Step through the Front Door into an Enclosed Foyer that Serves as a Gracious Transition between the Outside World and the Cozy Interior. Tall Ceilings Immediately Greet You While a Plethora of Windows Invites Plenty Of Natural Light.  The Newly Renovated, Open Concept Kitchen Flows into a Formal Dining Space or Family Room! Hardwood Floors,  Gas Heat, Newer Roof, Brand New Central Air Conditioning are just some of the Updates. The Fully Finished Basement Hosts the Updated Electric Panel and Has Access to the Backyard!  The Charm Extends Outdoors to a Private Backyard Retreat. Enjoy the Private Patio Surrounded by Lush Greenery, Providing the Perfect Setting for Outdoor Dining and Relaxation.  Complete With a FirePit for those Chilly Nights!
